            </h2>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 md:mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
                AetherMeet lets you create temporary, secure chat rooms with sensible passwords and democratic admission controls. <strong>Try it instantly - no signup required!</strong>
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 justify-center items-center mb-16 md:mb-24 px-4">
                <!-- Primary CTA: Demo Room -->
                <button id="demoBtn" class="btn-brutal btn-brutal-primary px-8 md:px-12 py-4 font-black tracking-normal text-base md:text-lg w-full md:w-auto" data-i18n="nav.startDemoRoom">
                    Start Demo Room
                </button>
                <!-- Secondary CTAs -->
